                            </p>
                            <div class="quotes rightquotes">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col3 corner">
                            <div class="photo-container">
                                <div class="photo-caption corner">
                                    Brian Hartsock <span>(Happy camper)</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="photo-content">
                                    <img src="../../Content/images/hartsock.jpg" alt="Profile photo" />
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-footer-container">
        <div class="nav-footer-container-inner">
            <div class="nav-footer">
                <span class="copyright">Created by Brian Hartsock</span>
                <ul>
                    <li class="first"><a href="http://blog.brianhartsock.com">My Blog</a></li>
                    <li class="first"><a href="http://twitter.com/brianhartsock">My Twitter</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
